However, since we left the `...` inside our theme, we can pass additional arguments into the `basic_theme()`. Let's change the column label background to red.

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
mtcars %>% 
  head() %>% 
  gt() %>% 
  basic_theme(
    column_labels.background.color = "red"
  )
```

